  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/187ef25f3f9142d94a2c1a153d6e153e.webp?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pals Go Only Up!</strong> is a very very difficult platform game. Jump, fall, yell at your cat (don't); climb your way to the top and unfold the mystery of <strong>The Island</strong>. There are no checkpoints; but many long falls, difficult jumps, and a long way down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/5d97b1251d5d77fd82236873f46d339b.poster.avif?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/5d97b1251d5d77fd82236873f46d339b.webm?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/5d97b1251d5d77fd82236873f46d339b.mp4?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/952dc172c47ee4aad5db628d52d70c22.webp?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is all about testing your skills and reflexes. Each level gets tougher, so you'll need to stay focused and keep your cool. And hey, if you're a streamer, even better! Your audience will love watching you tackle the ups and downs of <strong>Pals Go Only Up!</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/831b8924657c3d545978f48d19e6af90.poster.avif?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/831b8924657c3d545978f48d19e6af90.webm?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/831b8924657c3d545978f48d19e6af90.mp4?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/eef180f06ec984062b57de153cc9f2ed.webp?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, what do you say? Ready to take on the challenge and reach the top? Let's climb!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/d641259ec4d9abe0ab7a63466354d60e.poster.avif?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/d641259ec4d9abe0ab7a63466354d60e.webm?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/d641259ec4d9abe0ab7a63466354d60e.mp4?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/187ef25f3f9142d94a2c1a153d6e153e.webp?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pals Go Only Up!</strong> is a very very difficult platform game. Jump, fall, yell at your cat (don't); climb your way to the top and unfold the mystery of <strong>The Island</strong>. There are no checkpoints; but many long falls, difficult jumps, and a long way down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/5d97b1251d5d77fd82236873f46d339b.poster.avif?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/5d97b1251d5d77fd82236873f46d339b.webm?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/5d97b1251d5d77fd82236873f46d339b.mp4?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/952dc172c47ee4aad5db628d52d70c22.webp?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is all about testing your skills and reflexes. Each level gets tougher, so you'll need to stay focused and keep your cool. And hey, if you're a streamer, even better! Your audience will love watching you tackle the ups and downs of <strong>Pals Go Only Up!</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/831b8924657c3d545978f48d19e6af90.poster.avif?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/831b8924657c3d545978f48d19e6af90.webm?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/831b8924657c3d545978f48d19e6af90.mp4?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/eef180f06ec984062b57de153cc9f2ed.webp?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, what do you say? Ready to take on the challenge and reach the top? Let's climb!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/d641259ec4d9abe0ab7a63466354d60e.poster.avif?t=1773967650\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/d641259ec4d9abe0ab7a63466354d60e.webm?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912420/extras/d641259ec4d9abe0ab7a63466354d60e.mp4?t=1773967650\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
